      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Beautiful mint-condition car that\u2019s been exceptionally well kept and really stands out for its clean presentation, excellent overall condition, and strong value compared with buying new. This is the kind of used car that\u2019s tough to find\u2014super clean inside and out, clearly cared for, and ready for its next owner to enjoy. If you\u2019ve been waiting for a top-tier, turn-key vehicle, this one is absolutely worth a look.",
