      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "$33,900 - A well-kept, good-condition car that\u2019s ready to enjoy and offers a great balance of style, usability, and value. It presents nicely overall, has clearly been cared for, and should make a very appealing choice for someone who wants a solid example without paying mint-condition money. Expect normal signs of use consistent with a good, honest car, but overall it shows well and has plenty to like.",
